# Generated report outputs.
#
# Every Phase 1 audit / reconciliation / backfill / verification script
# rewrites these files on each run. Tracking them in git was an early-
# Phase-1 mistake: it caused merge / pull conflicts on every operator
# machine that produced its own runs.
#
# Source-of-truth is the script + the database, not the artefact.
# Operators archive the JSON/MD outputs to a security-tracked location
# (or an internal storage bucket) per `SAAS_PHASE1_EXECUTION_RUNBOOK.md`.

# Ignore every generated report
phase1/*.json
phase1/*.md
phase1-real/*.json
phase1-real/*.md

# But keep the README explaining the directory
!phase1/README.md
!phase1-real/README.md
